</li><li> Normal pink hearts accompany Belkar's seduction of a female bard in <a class="urllink" href="http://www.giantitp.com/comics/oots0611.html">#611<img src="https://static.tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pub/external_link.gif" height="12" width="12" style="border:none;"></a>.
