</li><li> <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Webcomic/TheCyantianChronicles" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Webcomic/TheCyantianChronicles">The Cyantian Chronicles</a></em>: Seen in Campus Safari when Cilke first met <span class="spoiler" title="you can set spoilers visible by default on your profile"> Chrome.</span> They were immediately dubbed "Floaty Love Hearts" by a fan of the comic.
